{"tid":2218181,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《下民易虐，上天難欺》 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-09-26T04:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:17:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff662e1dcb8f74fd7bf99929a9dc4310086276f","tid":2218181,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200926/Z3HCQNKD5ZFDTOJBPEFK2NYVW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200926%2FZ3HCQNKD5ZFDTOJBPEFK2NYVW4%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=df1ff337\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200926%2FZ3HCQNKD5ZFDTOJBPEFK2NYVW4%2F&h=e9102769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200926/Z3HCQNKD5ZFDTOJBPEFK2NYVW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《下民易虐，上天難欺》 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b3yO35cF4vZXQPAMFLPwfSMGZsY=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TOHQSTG7HRCMZNTRU2BM7JET7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb3yO35cF4vZXQPAMFLPwfSMGZsY%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTOHQSTG7HRCMZNTRU2BM7JET7M.jpg&h=48e39441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毓民新書《下民易虐，上天難欺》已經到我手中。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n過去一年多，從去年4月反送中開始，到今年6月30日，香港通過《港區國安法》，撕破「一國兩制」假面具，香港正式進入「黨國體制」，以專權取代民主體制。這期間發生過的每一件事，每一個真正的香港人都心知肚明。可是，歷史是勝利者的歷史，不管這「勝利」用甚麼樣的手段贏得，或者應該說，歷史是當權者著述的，香港人害怕真實的歷史被改寫，被遺忘，所以，包括毓民這樣的人紀錄了歷史，而不敢遺忘的人把它買回家。這正是這本書好賣的原因。2000本精裝一早售罄，平裝再版也所餘無幾。<br />\n<br />\n港府如何縱惡，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8db852ff8e7545eb5ab2c11c0c90447bb3210f12","tid":2218181,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff662e1dcb8f74fd7bf99929a9dc4310086276f","tid":2218181,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0